channel.title: Help with my server please
channel.description:
This randomly started happening, my players can connect and everything, but once the connection get's accepted the server just freezes and does nothing.
I really need help!!! Pic: [img]http://i326.photobucket.com/albums/k421/lesterknome/untitled-2.jpg[/img] It stops when it's making accounts, players that already have an account can get on fine, but it stops after what is shown EDIT: No New accounts can be made!!?!!?! :( :( :( IDC ANYMORE MUCH... IM BOERD THE FUCK OF LIFE. [center][img]http://www.moparisthebest.org/smf/Themes/default/images/warnwarn.gif[/img] Settle down, no need to be hysterical about a server. If you are really that frustrated, get off the computer and go take a small walk and then come back. You will feel much better.[/center]
